==Y17==
The first World Championship Y17 was held in 1975, the next in 1979. It is worth noting, that the Soviet Union took part in both 1975 and 1979 but did not win a medal until the third installment in 1981. In 1995 and 1997 it was Y18 teams instead of Y17.<ref name=sbfp17>{{cite web|url=http://iof1.idrottonline.se/SvenskaBandyforbundet/Landslag/P17-landslaget/Historikochstatistik/|title=P17-landslaget: Historik och statistik|publisher=[[Swedish Bandy Association]]|accessdate=15 May 2014}}</ref>

