==Y19==
{{Main|Bandy World Championship Y-19}}
World Championship Y19 has been held biannually since 1968. In 1994 and 1996 it was Y20 teams instead.<ref name=sbfp19>{{cite web|url=http://iof1.idrottonline.se/SvenskaBandyforbundet/Landslag/P19-landslaget/Historikochstatistik/|title=P19-landslaget: Historik och statistik|publisher=[[Swedish Bandy Association]]|accessdate=15 May 2014}}</ref>

