==Y23==
{{Main|Bandy World Championship Y-23}}
World Championship Y23 were held in 1990 and in 1992, but then the next was not held until 2011.<ref name=sbfu23>{{cite web|url=http://iof1.idrottonline.se/SvenskaBandyforbundet/Landslag/U23-landslaget/Historikochstatistik/|title=U23-landslaget: Historik och statistik|publisher=[[Swedish Bandy Association]]|accessdate=15 May 2014}}</ref>

===Champions===
* 1990 {{flagicon|Soviet Union}} Soviet Union<ref name=sbfu23/>
* 1992 {{flagicon|Sweden}} Sweden<ref name=sbfu23/>
* 2011 {{flagicon|Russia}} Russia<ref name=bandysidan/>
* 2013 {{flagicon|Russia}} Russia<ref name=bandysidan/>
* 2016 {{flagicon|Sweden}} Sweden

